show.description: A fearless young woman agrees to marry a cold, powerful man as a stand-in bride — but soon proves she's no substitute. As sparks fly and secrets unfold, she turns a fake marriage into a battle of hearts and pride. Watch "The Female Lead is the Strongest Mouthpiece Substitute" now!
